Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然想拍我們的照片了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想送去給在汐入的千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小啪的好朋友是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拍到玉響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在這種普通的地方拍到也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  這裡要推倒才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  剛剛你按快門了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會拍到玉響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年春天  我離開了出生的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入讀了這個令人懷念的小鎮的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在去世的父親所喜歡的這座小鎮裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次開始進行父親教給我的攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我不想讓開心的回憶染上悲哀的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在飄然而幸福的心情下所拍下到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的光之精靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是  玉響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個告訴我的也是父親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶有玉響的照片能讓看的人也洋溢著幸福的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要用這相機來「Let's Photo」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:57.56,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,100)\fad(500,500)}「因為是我起點的小鎮」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}中學3年級的初夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵  這份照片集上次不也借過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是我又想看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼中意它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多天空的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看著就有種飄飄然的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄飄然？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是哪裡的天空呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜它多數是瀨戶內海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有很多小島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得  以前楓喵經常去的竹原市也在瀨戶內海那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要讓你回想起那什麼的  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學時交到的朋友千尋  為了不讓我因為父親的事而傷感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很為我費心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「打起精神來吧」  她一直這樣為我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍稍有些愛哭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.14,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒  我要拍照了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:34.40,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看爸爸這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.95,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.90,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  再來一張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:39.86,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我想起我有件急事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵陪我下  突然想起實在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了…快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋  急事是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你覺得這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風箏？小青蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老薑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗喲噗喲   新角色的噗喲助大王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗喲助？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  長著張很有意思的臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後請好好相處…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你為我操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵決定高中去哪裡讀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒  我在考慮該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們讀同一所高中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是這樣好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我英語進步很多了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得楓喵適合在海外進行活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的  你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為楓喵經常會顯得很有膽識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以去各個國家拍下各種照片來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…我不是故意要讓你想起來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是我先哭起來的  真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我也因此就不會再流淚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋是我的元氣來源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對了  除了噗喲助之外我還在想些其他的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我完成後你能來看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我只要看著父親的照片和相機就會感到悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都被我封存起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋說我拍的照片很有趣  她很喜歡的這些回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及打算改日一起去竹原市的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也都被我封存起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓歡迎回來  我發現了爸爸的照片喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡在我悲傷深淵中的照片們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面所拍到的每一張都充滿著歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些難以忘懷的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從令人懷念而又無比親切的照片中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間噴湧出了按下快門時的父親的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼照片現在看起來都不再悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候發生改變的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個相機去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的那個相機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好好保存著喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個相機我能拿來用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:09:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等會拿出來給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這裡的相冊拿出去的是香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們一起看了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個杯子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在你父親生日的時候做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親教的東西我都還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶說過  父親一直都活在楓的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算現在因為悲痛而無法明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總有一天會發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親所教的事都存活在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定還有好多好多其他的東西留在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  小香  我們去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算繼續開始攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這相機是你父親的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昨天我讓媽媽拿出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  太好了  楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧了千尋為我加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:12:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…太好了…又
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一張照片我要拍千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要拍了哦  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵果然好能放得開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓  學校那邊沒問題  奶奶去確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香也喜歡那個小鎮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小楓去的話我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香還要轉學呢  我一個人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那乾脆就搬家過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家～搬家～搬家～搬家～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:08.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵果然很有膽識啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我媽媽的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那已經決定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  明明都說過去同一所高中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵好厲害噗喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了  噗喲助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然稍稍會有點寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是楓喵自己決定的事讓我覺得很高興噗喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要為你加油噗喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用笑臉來歡送你噗喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT  噗嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會送信來的哦噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了  音噗嚕  紐露造  瑪噼摩噼摩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親那邊沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  現在的工作再有2個月就能設法完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽決定放棄現在的工作  到那邊和奶奶一起經營店舖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說原來媽媽就夢想著能經營家咖啡店的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  寄給攝影家的志寶美理穗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道會不會有回信…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  有沒有聯繫過小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  信已經寄出了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我要去她那裡讀高中後很是吃驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要打個電話試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直都是信件來往的  感覺會很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道小薰和佐代美姐姐長成什麼樣子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  真是期待再次見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然媽媽是這麼說  但老實說我還是有些不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是不是能和以前一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  楓喵  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回…回…回信了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡小姐的母親和妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話那頭的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有留下相機的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及按下快門的澤渡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎澤渡小姐最喜歡的家人都被保存進了那張照片裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常幸福的瞬間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特意回信  還真是個不錯的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把這個都一起放進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有到達站…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有寫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追記  我也最喜歡瀨戶內了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜燒是不放烏賊天的那派
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}烏賊天，一種裹麵粉油炸烏賊的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  章魚的天婦羅最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是不是護身符之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵  感覺你好像變了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  似乎變得積極了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積極？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  膽識在不斷提升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人不敢給專業攝影師寄照片的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是因為你再次拿起了那相機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧  我想是不是楓喵你的父親給了你力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到楓喵再次開始攝影  最開心的應該就是你父親了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不在同一所學校了  我們都要變得積極起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  變得積極起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然覺得還有不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:18:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是回首望去  那些時間短得讓人覺得心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝願千尋入學考試能夠合格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝願楓喵\N不搞錯考試日期、不忘帶東西、不在車站迷路的情況下到達考場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且不填錯問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  明天終於要前往那個令人懷念的小鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨時起意的裝扮  你覺得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這樣的楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這是給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多…多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一組新角色的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情如火的幸運角色  普利莉安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴守時間的  哈維利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒疲憊的  悠露咩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有它在就不會迷路的  魚龍符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人安心的  笑呵呵先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿那麼多我不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學考試要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實還有個禮物在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有自信不敢拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要的話請不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相冊和相機包  連車票的袋子都有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵  一路保重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會為你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:20:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  沒有流著淚為你送行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋很陽光喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好  路上小心喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要自己前往竹原
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用父親以前帶我們去的方式  換乘電車前往那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:35.07,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到達三原站了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我所熟悉的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  大海好近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海邊玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和小薰她們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從電車裡看出去的風景一成未變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都和那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在回來了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了父親所在的那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小鎮應該發生了不少變化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定也有我不認識的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是會…緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼  稍稍有些吃驚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候  我似乎覺得這小鎮一直都在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的景色已經不復存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們都畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.17,0:24:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋說她總有一天會來這裡玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.96,0:24:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  玉響～hitotose～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.76,0:24:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為是被溫柔的香氣所包圍的日子」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
